@startuml user-journey-login
!theme plain

participant User as U
participant System as S

U ->> S: Click login button
S ->> U: Display login form
U ->> S: Enter credentials
S ->> S: Validate credentials
S ->> U: Grant access

note right of U
  Login Section
  - User interaction
  - Credential entry
  - Access granted
end note

@enduml
